text:
Portnoy, who made sure to point out that his nickname is “El Presidente,” asked if the actual president ever tweets something out and then wakes up the next day and thinks, “Aw man, I wish I didn’t send that one out.” 

“Often,” Trump replied. “Too often.” https://t.co/WmuXX4tcNQ
